text: M. taiwanensis may refer to: * Maackia taiwanensis, a legume species found only in Taiwan * Macrothele taiwanensis, a mygalomorph spider species in the genus Macrothele * Methanocalculus taiwanensis, an Archaea species in the genus Methanocalculus * Myotis taiwanensis, a bat species
title: M. taiwanensis
